---
layout: base.njk
title: Wheel Fitment Comparison Calculator
description: Compare wheel fitment between different widths and offsets. Check arch and strut clearance differences before buying new wheels.
navActive: fitment
---
<!-- Mobile tab bar -->
<div class="tab-bar">
  <button class="mobile-tab tab-btn tab-btn-active" data-tab="tab-calculator">Calculator</button>
  <button class="mobile-tab tab-btn" data-tab="tab-results">Results</button>
  <button class="mobile-tab tab-btn" data-tab="tab-about">About</button>
</div>

<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6">
<div class="lg:flex-shrink-0">

<!-- Tab: Calculator -->
<div class="tab-panel" id="tab-calculator">
<div id="offset-calculator" class="calc-card">
<h3 class="calc-heading">Wheel Details (old vs. new)</h3>
<form onsubmit="calculator.calculateFitment(this); return false;" onreset="calculator.clearall();">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
  <div class="calc-field">
    <label for="wheelWidth" class="calc-label-old">Old wheel <em class="uppercase not-italic">width</em></label>
    <span class="calc-unit">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="wheelWidth" name="wheelWidth" size="4" class="calc-input bg-[#FFE4B5]" />
  </div>
  <div class="calc-field">
    <label for="offset" class="calc-label-old">Old wheel <em class="uppercase not-italic">offset</em></label>
    <span class="calc-unit">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="offset" name="offset" size="4" class="calc-input bg-[#FFE4B5]" />
  </div>
  <div class="calc-field">
    <label for="newWheelWidth" class="calc-label-new">New wheel <em class="uppercase not-italic">width</em></label>
    <span class="calc-unit">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="newWheelWidth" name="newWheelWidth" size="4" class="calc-input bg-[#FFE4B5]" />
  </div>
  <div class="calc-field">
    <label for="newOffset" class="calc-label-new">New wheel <em class="uppercase not-italic">offset</em></label>
    <span class="calc-unit">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="newOffset" name="newOffset" size="4" class="calc-input bg-[#FFE4B5]" />
  </div>
  <div class="calc-field">
    <label for="diameter" class="calc-label">Wheel diameter</label>
    <span class="calc-unit">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="diameter" name="diameter" size="4" class="calc-input bg-[#F0F0F0]" />
  </div>
  <div class="calc-field">
    <label for="spacers" class="calc-label">Spacers</label>
    <span class="calc-unit">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="spacers" name="spacers" size="4" value="0" class="calc-input bg-[#F0F0F0]" />
  </div>
</div>
<div class="calc-controls">
  <input type="submit" class="button" value="Calculate" />&nbsp;
  <input type="reset" class="button" value="Reset" />
</div>
</form>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Tab: Results -->
<div class="tab-panel hidden lg:block" id="tab-results">
<table id="offset-calculator-result" class="results w-full text-sm mb-4">
<tr><th></th><th>Old</th><th>New</th></tr>
<tr><th>Wheel Width <span class="text-xs font-normal">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span></th>
<td id="old-width">-</td><td id="new-width">-</td></tr>
<tr><th>Wheel Offset <span class="text-xs font-normal">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span></th>
<td id="old-offset">-</td><td id="new-offset">-</td></tr>
<tr><th>Overall Offset <span class="text-xs font-normal">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span></th>
<td>-</td><td id="overall-offset">-</td></tr>
<tr><th>Arch clearance <span class="text-xs font-normal">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span></th>
<td>-</td><td id="arch-diff">-</td></tr>
<tr><th>Strut clearance <span class="text-xs font-normal">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span></th>
<td>-</td><td id="strut-diff">-</td></tr>
</table>
<div id="comparison" class="results"></div>
<div id="resource-links" class="results text-right text-xs"></div>
<a class="tab-back hidden" onclick="goBack()">&#8592; Back</a>
</div>

</div>

<!-- Tab: About -->
<div class="tab-panel hidden lg:block" id="tab-about">
<div id="description" class="about-panel">
<h2 class="about-heading">About the Wheel Fitment Calculator</h2>
<p><img src="/images/wheel.jpg" width="300" alt="Wheel Calculator" class="rounded shadow-md mb-4" /></p>
<p class="mb-4">The wheel fitment calculator allows you to compare the arch and strut clearance of two different wheels.</p>
<p class="mb-4">The calculator also provides a comparison of the new wheel against other wheel sizes with the same arch clearance.</p>
<p class="mb-4">For example, you can see that a 9.5J et12 wheel has 37mm less arch clearance than an 8J et30 wheel; which is equivalent to having an 8J et-7 or 11J et31 wheel.</p>
<p><a href="javascript:switchTab('tab-calculator'); calculator.demo('wheel-fitment', 0);" class="about-link">Click for a demo!</a></p>
